name: Bootie Liscious
description:
Single cotton pink and white bootie
Trafalgar Square, London, UK
18 July 2018

Victoria plans a complex stealth manoeuvre as walkers rush to and fro. Plagued by doubt, dare she even try?
Clara's bootie lies alone in Trafalgar Square, while all around mill and mass. 

-----

The Lost Shoe Project brings together participants from around the world, in a performance piece documented in close-to-real-time as a sequence of photographic images of lost or abandoned shoes. The Collector presents this first array of his most loved images.
